sequenceDiagram
    participant Ext as External content
    participant Wake as Wake bridge
    participant MainLoop as GLFW main loop
    participant DL as Display list
    participant Post as Post-composite pass

    Ext->>Wake: on_frame_ready or MutationObserver dirty
    Wake->>Wake: mark video_frame_pending or webview dirty
    Wake->>MainLoop: wake via glfwPostEmptyEvent
    MainLoop->>MainLoop: unblock glfwWaitEventsTimeout
    MainLoop->>MainLoop: webview_manager_poll_dirty re-snapshots layers
    MainLoop->>DL: render walk emits video and webview placeholders
    DL->>Post: render_video_frames scans placeholders
    Post->>Post: rdt_video_get_frame then blit plus controls overlay
    Post->>MainLoop: clear video_frame_pending then swap buffers
